                            oc:textContent "This skill enables precise extraction of text, tables, and metadata from PDF documents using **pdfplumber** - the go-to library for PDF data extraction. Unlike basic PDF readers, pdfplumber provides detailed character-level positioning, accurate table detection, and visual debugging." ] ;
